Title: Namal Institute
Paragraph: Please visit our fundraising website below:

The Quality Enhancement Cell (QEC) at Namal is an independent body that reviews, critiques and gives feedback on current academic practices. The QEC creates mechanisms and activities to ensure and enhance the quality of academic life at Namal and continually pushes for quality within academia. Our working principle centres on ensuring a culture of dignity and respect at the workplace shall engender quality work from the members of community as a natural consequence.
